grading(100) = writing assignments(70) + oral presentation(30)

1. writing assignments
- each write-up should be self-contained and focused
- to be written in latex
- latex source files to be uploaded at a public space (can be anonymous)
- source files will be made private after the semester
- deadlines: 3/22, 4/5, 4/19, 5/3, 5/17, by 6pm

2. oral presentation
- replaces the final exam
- presentation should be based on one's own writing assignments
- will take place no later than 6/12

3. grading policy
- A: 91-100
- B: 81-90
- C: 71-80
